| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0882 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 92e67e19-2039-5e9e-b1a2-f0f740d8cfa9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
